course.subject: BIOEE
course.course_title: Special Topics in Ocean Biodiversity: Ocean Biodiversity Research Apprenticeship

notes.note: Prerequisites: Intro Biology or Intro Oceanography, and permission of instructor. This course is part of an off campus program at Friday Harbor Marine Labs that provides field research experience for advanced students in marine biology. You must apply to be accepted to the program by contacting the course coordinator Reyn Yoshioka (rmy27@cornell.edu).
